BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/cali400-37.html
Competition: Juegos del Cuarto Centenario de Cali
Season: 1937

*NB: games of the 4th Centenary of Cali
*Held at the Estadio de San Fernando, now the Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero.

* Independiente Rivadavia : the club Independiente Rivadavia of Mendoza
* Colombia  : a national selection
* Cuba      : the champion club Deportivo Centro Gallego, reinforced
* Ecuador   : a selection from Ambato
* Jalisco XI    : a selection from Jalisco state
* Panama    : a national selection (prior to the formation of the national federation)
*Peru withdrew.

*Known results:

7/20/1937; Colombia ; 3-1; Jalisco XI; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

7/21/1937; Deportivo Centro Gallego XI     ; 9-3; Ambato XI; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

7/22/1937; Independiente Rivadavia; 5-1; Panama; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

7/23/1937; Deportivo Centro Gallego XI     ; 3-0; Jalisco XI; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero
Notes: Deportivo Centro Gallego XIn player Sergio Alonso was injured fatally in this match

7/24/1937; Colombia ; 1-3; Independiente Rivadavia; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

7/25/1937; Ambato XI  ; 4-0; Panama; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

7/27/1937; Independiente Rivadavia; 3-1; Jalisco XI; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

7/28/1937; Colombia ; 5-0; Ambato XI; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

7/29/1937; Jalisco XI   ; 2-2; Panama; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

7/31/1937; Deportivo Centro Gallego XI     ; 2-0; Independiente Rivadavia; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

8/1/1937 Colombia;  1-3; Deportivo Centro Gallego XI; Estadio Olímpico Pascual Guerrero

